<inglise> COMMISSION REGULATION (EC) No 1426/98 of 3 July 1998 fixing the maximum amount of compensatory aid for the appreciable revaluation of the pound sterling on 3 May 1998 </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (E&Uuml;) nr 1426/98, milles m&auml;&auml;ratakse 3. mail 1998 toimunud naelsterlingi m&auml;rgatava revalveerimise tulemusel makstava tasandustoetuse &uuml;lemm&auml;&auml;r 3. juuli 1998 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Community, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa &Uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EC) No 724/97 of 22 April 1997 determining measures and compensation relating to appreciable revaluations that affect farm incomes (1), as last amended by Regulation (EC) No 942/98 (2), and in particular Article 7 thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 22. aprilli 1997. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (E&Uuml;) nr 724/97 (millega m&auml;&auml;ratakse kindlaks p&otilde;llumajandustulusid m&otilde;jutava m&auml;rgatava revalveerimisega seotud meetmed ja tasandustoetus, (1) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 942/98 (2)) eriti selle artiklit 7, </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Regulation (EC) No 724/97 lays down that the Member States may grant aid to farmers to compensate for an appreciable revaluation; whereas such compensatory aid is to be granted under the conditions indicated in that Regulation and in Commission Regulation (EC) No 805/97 of 2 May 1997 laying down detailed rules for compensation relating to appreciable revaluations (3); </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: m&auml;&auml;ruses (E&Uuml;) nr 724/97 s&auml;testatakse, et liikmesriigid v&otilde;ivad m&auml;&auml;rata talupidajatele toetusi m&auml;rgatava revalveerimise h&uuml;vitamiseks; selline tasandustoetus tuleb m&auml;&auml;rata vastavalt k&otilde;nealuses m&auml;&auml;ruses ja komisjoni 2. mai 1997. aasta m&auml;&auml;ruses (E&Uuml;) nr 805/97 (milles s&auml;testatakse m&auml;rgatava revalveerimisega seotud tasandustoetuse &uuml;ksikasjalikud eeskirjad) (2) s&auml;testatud tingimustele; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the amount of compensatory aid is calculated in accordance with Articles 4, 5 and 6 of Regulation (EC) No 724/97 and includes a principal amount and, where appropriate, supplementary amounts under the second subparagraph of Article 3(2) of that Regulation; </inglise>
<eesti> tasandustoetus arvutatakse vastavalt m&auml;&auml;ruse (E&Uuml;) nr 724/97 artiklitele 4, 5 ja 6 ning see sisaldab p&otilde;hisummat ja vajaduse korral k&otilde;nealuse m&auml;&auml;ruse artikli 3 l&otilde;ike 2 teise l&otilde;igu kohaseid lisasummasid; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, to facilitate the preparations for granting this compensatory aid, the maximum principal amount of the first instalment thereof should be fixed on the basis of the latest data available on the sterling pound revaluation that occurred on 3 May 1998; whereas this maximum amount is established without prejudice to a reduction or cancellation in case of an increase in the agricultural conversion rate in the observation period referred to in Article 4(3) of Regulation (EC) No 724/97, without prejudice to account being taken of the situation on the market in the same observation period and without prejudice to the possibility of granting supplementary amounts under the second subparagraph of Article 3(2) of that Regulation; </inglise>
<eesti> k&otilde;nealuse tasandustoetuse m&auml;&auml;ramise ettevalmistamise h&otilde;lbustamiseks tuleks esimese osamakse p&otilde;hisumma &uuml;lemm&auml;&auml;r kinnitada 3. mail 1998 toimunud naelsterlingi revalveerimise kohta saadaolevate viimaste andmete p&otilde;hjal; k&otilde;nealune &uuml;lemm&auml;&auml;r kinnitatakse, ilma et see piiraks selle alandamist v&otilde;i t&uuml;histamist m&auml;&auml;ruse (E&Uuml;) nr 724/97 artikli 4 l&otilde;ikes 3 osutatud vaatlusperioodi jooksul toimunud p&otilde;llumajandusliku &uuml;mberarvestuskursi t&otilde;usu puhul ning ilma et see piiraks samal vaatlusperioodil turuolukorra arvessev&otilde;tmist ning v&otilde;imalust m&auml;&auml;rata k&otilde;nealuse m&auml;&auml;ruse artikli 3 l&otilde;ike 2 teise l&otilde;igu kohaselt lisasummasid; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, to apply Regulation (EC) No 805/97, the period referred to in Article 3(1) of that Regulation must be specified so that the aid is linked to previous production; </inglise>
<eesti> m&auml;&auml;ruse (E&Uuml;) nr 805/97 kohaldamiseks tuleb t&auml;psustada k&otilde;nealuse m&auml;&auml;ruse artikli 3 l&otilde;ikes 1 osutatud ajavahemik nii, et toetus oleks seotud varasema toodanguga; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the measures provided for in this Regulation are in accordance with the opinion of the relevant management committees, </inglise>
<eesti> k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;rusega etten&auml;htud meetmed on koosk&otilde;las asjaomaste korralduskomiteede arvamusega, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> For the United Kingdom, the principal amount of the first instalment of compensatory aid within the meaning of Article 1(2) of Regulation (EC) No 805/97 shall be a maximum of ECU 2,1 million in the case of the appreciable revaluation that occurred on 3 May 1998. </inglise>
<eesti> &Uuml;hendkuningriigi puhul on m&auml;&auml;ruse (E&Uuml;) nr 805/97 artikli 1 l&otilde;ike 2 kohase tasandustoetuse esimese osamakse p&otilde;hisumma &uuml;lemm&auml;&auml;r 3. mail 1998 toimunud m&auml;rgatava revalveerimise puhul 2,1 miljonit ek&uuml;&uuml;d. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> The amount fixed by this Regulation is established without prejudice to the effects of Article 4(3) of Regulation (EC) No 724/97. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolevas m&auml;&auml;ruses kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ratud summa kinnitatakse nii, et see ei piiraks m&auml;&auml;ruse (E&Uuml;) nr 724/97 artikli 4 l&otilde;ike 3 toimet. </eesti>
<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> To grant the compensatory aid the maximum amount of which is fixed by this Regulation, the period referred to in Article 3(1) of Regulation (EC) No 805/97 shall end on 30 April 1998 at the latest. </inglise>
<eesti> Selle tasandusteotuse m&auml;&auml;ramiseks, mille &uuml;lemm&auml;&auml;r on m&auml;&auml;ratud kindlaks k&auml;esolevas m&auml;&auml;ruses, l&otilde;ppeb m&auml;&auml;ruse (E&Uuml;) nr 805/97 artikli 3 l&otilde;ikes 1 osutatud ajavahemik hiljemalt 30. aprillil 1998. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 3 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 3 </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall enter into force on the seventh day following its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus j&otilde;ustub seitsmendal p&auml;eval p&auml;rast selle avaldamist Euroopa &Uuml;henduste Teatajas. </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus on tervikuna siduv ja vahetult kohaldatav k&otilde;ikides liikmesriikides. </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Brussels, 3 July 1998. </inglise>
<eesti> Br&uuml;ssel, 3. juuli 1998 </eesti>
